Based on LMWA, Na+ is expected to form the tightest pair with acetate ion [7,58]. On plotting the difference between hydration enthalpy of each cation and acetate ion against the corresponding Kd value for the ion pair (Fig. 8
                     ), a good correlation was found for monovalent cations except for Li+ and NH4
                     +. In fact, these ions bind more strongly than this model would predict.
